    "description": "<strong>Gehinnom 是一款随机生成的多人恐怖游戏，适合 1-4 名玩家。<br>通过举行仪式来驱逐追赶你的恶魔。 你必须通过收集从解决各种随机任务中获得的线索来找出仪式所需的物品。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/b3fe591f9fb2de3a9c2acfca6bb12c68.avif?t=1699088590\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/f7fcaa0d0355fb66e3e79a978ac4bb70.poster.avif?t=1699088590\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/f7fcaa0d0355fb66e3e79a978ac4bb70.webm?t=1699088590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/f7fcaa0d0355fb66e3e79a978ac4bb70.mp4?t=1699088590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>在Gehinnom中，由于游戏在各个方面都完全依赖随机性，从房间布局和道路到家具放置、线索位置、任务、跳跃恐惧、恶魔的攻击模式、陷阱，甚至是最小的细节，如 路上的岩石和不可预测的天气。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/709d61c49e61a6dc2f4a6c9470224b48.avif?t=1699088590\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/3559e63bdc61da31c1ad0c92729aa11d.poster.avif?t=1699088590\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/3559e63bdc61da31c1ad0c92729aa11d.webm?t=1699088590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/3559e63bdc61da31c1ad0c92729aa11d.mp4?t=1699088590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gehinnom 还具有 PvP 模式，其中一名玩家成为恶魔并在玩家完成仪式之前追捕他们。<br>作为恶魔玩家，你以幽灵的形式开始游戏，当你利用人类玩家周围的环境来恐吓他们时，你的出生条就会填满。<br>此外，每个人类玩家都有自己的恐惧表，当他们遇到可怕的情况时，恐惧表就会上升，恐惧表达到 100% 的玩家会非常容易受到你的攻击。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/5c18eba504a4332d0c1d8932e3e43d89.avif?t=1699088590\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/a737a80b4f1e067f170d4d5e8942d8cb.poster.avif?t=1699088590\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/a737a80b4f1e067f170d4d5e8942d8cb.webm?t=1699088590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/a737a80b4f1e067f170d4d5e8942d8cb.mp4?t=1699088590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>即使在死亡后，您的贡献对于仪式的成功仍然至关重要。<br>作为幽灵玩家，您仍然可以完成一些任务并与您的团队沟通以提供有关线索和物品位置的信息。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712050/extras/856dd3a6209920257c41b30993d69172.avif?t=1699088590\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>公共及私人大堂<br></li><li>语音聊天（近距离）和聊天框<br></li><li>控制器支持（XBOX/PS）<br></li><li>按键绑定<br></li><li>成就<br></li><li>动态天气<br></li><li>硬核模式<br></li><li>秘密</li></ul>",
